  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      comparing the effect of conventional mandibular single denture with flexible mandibular
      single denture on tissue and patient's satisfaction
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      comparing the effect of conventional mandibular single denture with flexible mandibular
      single denture on tissue by keratinization index through PAP stain and patient's satisfaction
